              <h2>Colorsy &#8211; Responsive Bootstrap Colorful Theme</h2>
              
                <p class="meta"><i class="icon-calendar"></i> 12 Mar 13 - <i class="icon-user"></i> Asho - <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://responsivewebinc.com/bootstrap-themes-2/colorsy-responsive-bootstrap-colorful-theme/#comments" title="Comment on Colorsy &#8211; Responsive Bootstrap Colorful Theme">1 Comment</a></p>


                <p><a href="http://responsivewebinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/responsive-bootstrap-colorful-theme.png"><img src="http://responsivewebinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/responsive-bootstrap-colorful-theme.png" alt="responsive bootstrap colorful theme" width="590" height="369" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-743" /></a></p>
<h3>Colorsy &#8211; Responsive Colorful Bootstrap Theme</h3>
<p>Colorsy is a professional bootstrap theme crafted with love. Colorsy comes in two version which are front end and portfolio. It has lots of cool features like colorful hero unit, image effects, responsive navigation bars, stylish portfolio, etc., So don&#8217;t miss the great theme. Download it now.</p>
<p><strong>Features (Front end):</strong></p>
<p> &#8211; Lots of colors.<br />
 &#8211; 28 HTML files.<br />
 &#8211; Professional Hero Unit ever made.<br />
 &#8211; Sidebar Navigation with dropdown support.<br />
 &#8211; Fully Responsive.<br />
 &#8211; Recent post slider and flex slider.<br />
 &#8211; Sliding boxes.<br />
 &#8211; Cool pages &#8211; Timeline, Coming soon, Make post, Tasks, Pricing table, etc.,<br />
 &#8211; 3 different blog styles.<br />
 &#8211; Supports Google web fonts, font awesome icons.</p>
<p><strong>Features (Portfolio):</strong></p>
<p> 1. Based on Colorsy Layout.<br />
 2. Colorful black theme with vertical and horizontal navigation (both has dropdown).<br />
 3. Sidebar widgets.<br />
 4. Footer widgets.<br />
 5. Cool isotope effects to showcase your images (works great on tablets and mobiles).<br />
 6. Page title with background image.<br />
 7. Lots of pages.<br />
 8. Supports almost all features of bootstrap. Also supports font awesome icon and google web fonts.</p>
<p><strong>Changelog:</strong></p>
<p><strong>Version 1.0:</strong></p>
<p> &#8211; Initial Release.</p>
